WEBVTT

1
00:01:14.286 --> 00:01:17.783
<b>I was told that I might not be able
to attend his entrance ceremony.</b>


2
00:01:20.380 --> 00:01:21.399
<b>But…</b>

3
00:01:24.016 --> 00:01:25.345
<b>I was able to go.</b>

4
00:01:32.358 --> 00:01:35.375
<b>I heard he was able to make friends.</b>

5
00:01:37.812 --> 00:01:40.270
<b>Surprisingly, he's quite sociable.</b>

6
00:01:43.537 --> 00:01:46.883
<b>I want to keep looking at him.</b>

7
00:01:48.012 --> 00:01:51.599
<b>A little more… Just a little longer.</b>

8
00:01:53.487 --> 00:01:56.524
<b>Even though, 
I already know that…</b>

9
00:02:31.639 --> 00:02:33.097
<b>Matsuri.</b>

10
00:02:35.605 --> 00:02:38.062
<b>Live until your last breath, alright?</b>

11
00:03:53.317 --> 00:04:03.307
<b>THE LAST 10 YEARS</b>

12
00:04:11.189 --> 00:04:14.166
<b>August 14, 2013.</b>

13
00:04:14.426 --> 00:04:16.194
<b>Weather is sunny.</b>

14
00:04:16.693 --> 00:04:19.191
<b>It's very sunny.</b>

15
00:04:21.489 --> 00:04:23.796
<b>I'm getting out of the hospital today!</b>

16
00:04:24.566 --> 00:04:28.631
<b>My very long hospital stay ends today.</b>

17
00:04:29.311 --> 00:04:33.217
<b>What are you doing, Matsuri?
Come help me.</b>


18
00:04:34.036 --> 00:04:37.533
<b>I'm a patient, but she never
holds back on me, my older sister, Kikyo.</b>


19
00:04:37.583 --> 00:04:39.291
<b>Really, you.</b>

20
00:04:39.590 --> 00:04:41.918
<b>Mom, your greetings
drag too long.</b>


21
00:04:42.018 --> 00:04:44.266
<b>- Start crying already.
- Alright, fine.</b>


22
00:04:44.506 --> 00:04:48.402
<b>Come by and say your thanks.
You've been taken care of by her!</b>


23
00:04:49.431 --> 00:04:50.699
<b>Good afternoon.</b>

24
00:04:51.089 --> 00:04:52.238
<b>Hello.</b>

25
00:04:52.328 --> 00:04:54.326
<b>Doctor Hirata.</b>

26
00:04:55.005 --> 00:04:56.903
<b>Thank you for taking care of me.</b>

27
00:04:57.103 --> 00:04:59.800
<b>Matsuri, congrats on your discharge.</b>

28
00:05:00.010 --> 00:05:02.817
<b>Doctor,
we really have been under your care</b>


29
00:05:02.897 --> 00:05:05.165
<b>- for such a long time.
- Not at all.</b>


30
00:05:06.524 --> 00:05:08.202
<b>Things are still about to start.</b>

31
00:05:12.807 --> 00:05:14.675
<b>Is that the Skytree?</b>

32
00:05:15.155 --> 00:05:17.153
<b>They finished it today.</b>

33
00:05:17.383 --> 00:05:20.170
<b>Really? It's so huge!</b>

34
00:05:20.649 --> 00:05:22.647
<b>I wanna go there.</b>

35
00:05:22.787 --> 00:05:23.986
<b>Hey, big sis.</b>

36
00:05:24.096 --> 00:05:27.463
<b>- Let's go there.
- I can't. I'm not good with heights.</b>


37
00:05:28.551 --> 00:05:30.280
<b>What are you afraid of
when I'm with you?</b>


38
00:05:30.400 --> 00:05:33.776
<b>My sister is saying she doesn't
want to take me to the Skytree!</b>


39
00:05:33.836 --> 00:05:36.014
<b>Come on, that's so sly of you.</b>

40
00:05:36.134 --> 00:05:38.082
<b>How long will you keep recording?
Hand it over!</b>


41
00:05:40.020 --> 00:05:42.458
<b>I haven't been to this house
for over 2 years.</b>


42
00:05:42.757 --> 00:05:44.306
<b>So nostalgic.</b>

43
00:05:44.446 --> 00:05:45.534
<b>Right.</b>

44
00:05:45.724 --> 00:05:46.813
<b>Come in.</b>

45
00:05:46.863 --> 00:05:48.482
<b>I'm home.</b>

46
00:06:07.722 --> 00:06:09.930
<b>It's tidier than it was two years ago.</b>

47
00:06:50.609 --> 00:06:53.147
<b>PULMONARY ARTERIAL HYPERTENSION</b>

48
00:07:01.878 --> 00:07:03.886
<b>A FATAL CONDITION</b>

49
00:07:01.878 --> 00:07:03.886
<b>NO RADICAL CURE</b>

50
00:07:06.224 --> 00:07:08.711
<b>FREQUENCY OF ONSET:

51
00:07:12.378 --> 00:07:14.565
<b>THERE IS A RISK OF SUDDEN DEATH</b>

52
00:07:29.470 --> 00:07:31.958
<b>ONLY 10 YEARS REMAINING</b>

53
00:07:45.564 --> 00:07:47.273
<b>Matsuri!</b>

54
00:07:50.899 --> 00:07:52.907
<b>We missed you so bad!</b>

55
00:07:52.977 --> 00:07:53.916
<b><i>Matsuri,</i></b>

56
00:07:53.956 --> 00:07:58.262
<b>- congratulations!
- Thank you!</b>


57
00:07:58.411 --> 00:08:00.669
<b>Alright.
Say, "cheese"!</b>


58
00:08:01.129 --> 00:08:03.956
<b>Yay! Thank you so much!</b>

59
00:08:04.116 --> 00:08:07.462
<b>This is the store manager, Mr. Akira.</b>

60
00:08:07.802 --> 00:08:09.740
<b>- Congratulations.
- I've been taken good care of.</b>


61
00:08:09.800 --> 00:08:12.318
<b>- Thank you so much.
- I'll slice the cake.</b>


62
00:08:12.847 --> 00:08:14.535
<b>- Here.
- Thank you so much.</b>


63
00:08:17.712 --> 00:08:18.861
<b>- That man?
- What?</b>


64
00:08:18.931 --> 00:08:20.210
<b>Was that your boyfriend?</b>

65
00:08:20.719 --> 00:08:21.868
<b>Yes.</b>

66
00:08:23.516 --> 00:08:25.135
<b>Seriously?!</b>

67
00:08:25.185 --> 00:08:27.802
<b>- What was that just now?
- What do you think?</b>


68
00:08:27.882 --> 00:08:30.210
<b>It's alright. 
No need to show off.</b>

69
00:08:31.578 --> 00:08:33.157
<b>I can't stand you!</b>

70
00:08:33.706 --> 00:08:36.983
<b>What I'm feeling right now
really takes me back!</b>


71
00:08:37.063 --> 00:08:38.991
<b>Almost like how it was in college.</b>

72
00:08:39.910 --> 00:08:40.999
<b>You're right.</b>

73
00:08:41.129 --> 00:08:43.716
<b>But, like, the university is too cruel!</b>

74
00:08:43.816 --> 00:08:46.343
<b>They didn't even hold a
special ceremony or something.</b>


75
00:08:46.413 --> 00:08:49.121
<b>True. We really wanted to
graduate with you, Matsuri.</b>


76
00:08:50.359 --> 00:08:51.668
<b>Thank you.</b>

77
00:08:53.237 --> 00:08:54.955
<b>Are you really alright now?</b>

78
00:08:56.044 --> 00:08:58.771
<b>I only need to go to the hospital
once a month now.</b>


79
00:08:59.460 --> 00:09:01.948
<b>I didn't think you'd get admitted
in the hospital this long!</b>


80
00:09:02.038 --> 00:09:03.916
<b>We seriously got worried for you.</b>

81
00:09:04.365 --> 00:09:07.263
<b>But you know, she's already discharged.</b>

82
00:09:07.892 --> 00:09:10.389
<b>Get a boyfriend
and work your ass off!</b>


83
00:09:10.489 --> 00:09:13.936
<b>Your life starts right now, seriously.
You need to put in more work!</b>


84
00:09:14.765 --> 00:09:15.754
<b>Oh, right.</b>

85
00:09:15.824 --> 00:09:18.411
<b>You know?
My company is too exploitative, I could die!</b>


86
00:09:18.481 --> 00:09:21.119
<b>"We're having a meeting right now,
so get here," like, so unbelievable!</b>


87
00:09:21.219 --> 00:09:22.627
<b>I'm not going.</b>

88
00:09:26.483 --> 00:09:28.931
<b>- See you!
- Bye-bye!</b>


89
00:09:32.967 --> 00:09:35.334
<b>Those two haven't changed.</b>

90
00:09:36.553 --> 00:09:38.881
<b>Will you be staying at home for now?</b>

91
00:09:40.999 --> 00:09:42.837
<b>That might be it.</b>

92
00:09:44.236 --> 00:09:46.104
<b>Oh, right.</b>

93
00:09:46.393 --> 00:09:48.272
<b>Are you no longer writing?</b>

94
00:09:48.581 --> 00:09:49.580
<b>What?</b>

95
00:09:50.220 --> 00:09:51.838
<b>Your novels.</b>

96
00:09:54.855 --> 00:09:56.923
<b>That's from a long time ago!</b>

97
00:09:57.003 --> 00:10:00.140
<b>I forgot about it while I was admitted in the hospital.
There's nothing to write about.</b>


98
00:10:00.230 --> 00:10:01.608
<b>What?</b>

99
00:10:02.437 --> 00:10:05.414
<b>I really loved everything you used to write.</b>

100
00:10:07.302 --> 00:10:08.421
<b>Right now,</b>

101
00:10:08.461 --> 00:10:11.009
<b>I'm working as a Column Editor,</b>

102
00:10:11.139 --> 00:10:13.556
<b>and people over there
haven't been getting enough sleep.</b>


103
00:10:14.226 --> 00:10:18.581
<b>If you're willing to work with us,
you'll come in handy right away.</b>


104
00:10:21.708 --> 00:10:23.606
<b>I might not be able to
live up to your expectations,</b>


105
00:10:23.686 --> 00:10:25.704
<b>and I don't want to
cause trouble on you.</b>


106
00:10:26.853 --> 00:10:28.721
<b>That's not true!</b>

107
00:10:34.355 --> 00:10:35.294
<b>Sorry.</b>

108
00:10:36.683 --> 00:10:37.992
<b>Dad?</b>

109
00:10:40.339 --> 00:10:41.968
<b>Yes, I see you.</b>

110
00:10:42.198 --> 00:10:43.396
<b>Alright.</b>

111
00:10:45.814 --> 00:10:47.083
<b>I gotta get going.</b>

112
00:10:47.662 --> 00:10:49.330
<b>Thanks for today!</b>

113
00:10:52.407 --> 00:10:55.664
<b>Once you feel like it,
reach out to me anytime.</b>


114
00:10:58.911 --> 00:11:00.209
<b>- See you.
- Bye-bye!</b>


115
00:11:05.175 --> 00:11:07.292
<b>- I'm home.
- Welcome back.</b>


116
00:11:07.372 --> 00:11:09.400
<b>How was your reunion with your friends?</b>

117
00:11:09.700 --> 00:11:11.298
<b>I had fun.</b>

118
00:11:12.207 --> 00:11:15.604
<b>Oh, right.
There's a delivery for you.</b>


119
00:11:41.089 --> 00:11:42.207
<b>What's that?</b>

120
00:11:42.557 --> 00:11:44.455
<b>Disability Annuity Payout?</b>

121
00:11:44.965 --> 00:11:47.212
<b>What? That's how much you're getting?!</b>

122
00:11:47.252 --> 00:11:49.630
<b>Making a fortune out from
my disability, you know?</b>


123
00:11:49.700 --> 00:11:51.268
<b>You dummy!</b>

124
00:11:56.573 --> 00:11:59.980
<b>From Mishima?
This brings me back!</b>


125
00:12:00.060 --> 00:12:01.748
<b>What? A class reunion?</b>

126
00:12:02.757 --> 00:12:05.644
<b>- Our first after reunion after graduating.
- Really?</b>


127
00:12:06.183 --> 00:12:08.371
<b>A class reunion sounds great.</b>

128
00:12:08.581 --> 00:12:11.009
<b>Reunite with people at the reunion,</b>

129
00:12:11.099 --> 00:12:13.946
<b>then you fall in love with someone,
which does happen at times.</b>


130
00:12:14.975 --> 00:12:16.543
<b>I'm not getting
into a relationship.</b>


131
00:12:17.892 --> 00:12:21.378
<b>There you go, saying that stuff again.</b>

132
00:12:24.355 --> 00:12:25.454
<b>But it does seem nice.</b>

133
00:12:26.763 --> 00:12:29.800
<b>I'm sure no one
knew that I was sick.</b>

134
00:12:36.064 --> 00:12:39.160
<b>The place for the Olympics
has finally been decided, huh?</b>


135
00:12:40.499 --> 00:12:43.166
<b><i>…which makes it 56 years since.</i></b>

136
00:12:43.696 --> 00:12:49.970
<b><i>What kind of tournament will the
Tokyo Olympics hold in seven years, in 2020?</i></b>


137
00:13:10.349 --> 00:13:12.917
<b>So nostalgic!</b>

138
00:13:14.056 --> 00:13:16.803
<b>First time since graduating
from middle school, huh?</b>


139
00:13:26.563 --> 00:13:28.751
<b>I hope everyone's well.</b>

140
00:13:30.959 --> 00:13:33.816
<b>If you don't feel good,
make sure you call me immediately.</b>


141
00:13:36.073 --> 00:13:37.542
<b>I know.</b>

142
00:13:53.266 --> 00:13:55.005
<b>Say something.</b>

143
00:13:56.173 --> 00:13:57.252
<b>Yeah,</b>

144
00:13:57.392 --> 00:13:59.210
<b>this does bring me back.</b>

145
00:14:00.199 --> 00:14:02.597
<b>How many times have you said that?</b>

146
00:14:03.116 --> 00:14:04.355
<b>Sorry.</b>

147
00:14:22.147 --> 00:14:24.985
<b>I'll be alright.</b>

148
00:14:51.328 --> 00:14:52.867
<b>That's too much!</b>

149
00:14:54.165 --> 00:14:55.794
<b>You changed too much!</b>

150
00:15:03.526 --> 00:15:04.835
<b>Are you not coming in?</b>

151
00:15:05.654 --> 00:15:07.762
<b>I'm sorry. Go ahead.</b>

152
00:15:10.829 --> 00:15:12.337
<b>Takabayashi?</b>

153
00:15:13.656 --> 00:15:15.684
<b>You are…?</b>

154
00:15:18.421 --> 00:15:20.939
<b>Matsuri?
It's you, right?!</b>


155
00:15:21.228 --> 00:15:22.517
<b>Miyuki?!</b>

156
00:15:22.597 --> 00:15:23.955
<b>It's been a while!</b>

157
00:15:24.875 --> 00:15:27.002
<b>You haven't changed at all!</b>

158
00:15:27.342 --> 00:15:28.831
<b>This way!
Everyone's here!</b>


159
00:15:35.734 --> 00:15:37.842
<b>Hey, Miyuki! 
Show us your child!</b>

160
00:15:38.291 --> 00:15:40.309
<b>- Here.
- Wait!</b>


161
00:15:40.998 --> 00:15:43.366
<b>- Seems like he's gotten bigger again!
- Yeah.</b>


162
00:15:43.476 --> 00:15:46.243
<b>He's so hard-headed,
I'm having a hard time!</b>


163
00:15:46.343 --> 00:15:48.091
<b>But, he's undeniably cute!</b>

164
00:15:48.191 --> 00:15:50.099
<b>No, he's such a monster!</b>

165
00:15:50.179 --> 00:15:53.306
<b>Hey, Matsuri! Matsuri!
You're in Tokyo too, right?</b>


166
00:15:54.435 --> 00:15:56.693
<b>Tokyo? I envy you!</b>

167
00:15:56.783 --> 00:15:59.030
<b>Matsuri, where are you working?</b>

168
00:15:59.800 --> 00:16:01.698
<b>Well…</b>

169
00:16:01.828 --> 00:16:04.455
<b>- Just an ordinary office worker.
- You have it good!</b>


170
00:16:04.495 --> 00:16:07.412
<b>An Office Lady at Tokyo.
What kind of work?</b>


171
00:16:08.431 --> 00:16:09.899
<b>Well…</b>

172
00:16:10.469 --> 00:16:12.237
<b>Publishing Industry.</b>

173
00:16:12.307 --> 00:16:14.535
<b>Publishing Industry?!</b>

174
00:16:14.984 --> 00:16:17.582
<b>Matsuri! You should join the group
next time for drinks!</b>


175
00:16:17.622 --> 00:16:19.070
<b>There you go!</b>

176
00:16:19.150 --> 00:16:22.347
<b>There's only 3 of us there!
Right, Kazuto? Kazu?</b>


177
00:16:22.447 --> 00:16:24.954
<b>Let's have a drink together at Tokyo
next time, us three!</b>


178
00:16:25.923 --> 00:16:27.722
<b>Wait, Manabe's
in Tokyo, too?</b>


179
00:16:27.812 --> 00:16:30.189
<b>Didn't you, like,
inherit your father's company?</b>


180
00:16:30.249 --> 00:16:34.325
<b>He is such a mystery!
If he did, his life would have been secured!</b>


181
00:16:34.405 --> 00:16:35.534
<b>But why?</b>

182
00:16:35.614 --> 00:16:37.492
<b>Well, I've got
my own circumstances.</b>


183
00:16:37.572 --> 00:16:39.600
<b>What do you mean by that?!</b>

184
00:16:39.700 --> 00:16:42.287
<b>Hey, Takeru! It's almost time
for the main event!</b>


185
00:16:42.357 --> 00:16:44.085
<b>Oh, right, right!</b>

186
00:16:44.605 --> 00:16:47.222
<b>Alright, everyone! Listen!
All eyes on me!</b>


187
00:16:47.881 --> 00:16:50.589
<b>Do you guys remember what this is?</b>

188
00:16:51.568 --> 00:16:53.756
<b>Our time capsule!</b>

189
00:16:55.923 --> 00:16:58.301
<b>For the future us!</b>

190
00:16:58.731 --> 00:17:02.547
<b>Once I call your name,
come up and claim yours!</b>


191
00:17:03.756 --> 00:17:05.134
<b>Kuro!</b>

192
00:17:05.214 --> 00:17:06.833
<b>Catch it!</b>

193
00:17:06.962 --> 00:17:08.561
<b>Hotpot right here!</b>

194
00:17:11.308 --> 00:17:12.996
<b>Alright, Matsuri!</b>

195
00:17:13.416 --> 00:17:14.745
<b>Here's yours.</b>

196
00:17:14.805 --> 00:17:17.012
<b>Alright, Manabe Kazuto.
Kazu!</b>


197
00:17:17.102 --> 00:17:18.371
<b>Here you go.</b>

198
00:17:19.710 --> 00:17:20.848
<b>This is no good.</b>

199
00:17:20.888 --> 00:17:22.826
<b>Alright, pass this around.</b>

200
00:17:20.888 --> 00:17:24.705
<b>TO ME, 10 YEARS LATER.</b>

201
00:17:20.888 --> 00:17:24.705
<b>ARE YOU DOING WELL?</b>

202
00:17:20.888 --> 00:17:24.705
<b>NOW THAT I'M 14,</b>

203
00:17:20.888 --> 00:17:24.705
<b>I'M SO HOOKED ABOUT</b>

204
00:17:20.888 --> 00:17:24.705
<b>STUDYING AND CLUB ACTIVITIES</b>

205
00:17:20.888 --> 00:17:24.705
<b>EVERY DAY.</b>

206
00:17:23.186 --> 00:17:24.705
<b>Pass it!</b>

207
00:17:27.362 --> 00:17:33.376
<b>HOWEVER, I AM HAVING FUN AND DOING MY BEST. 
WHAT KIND OF WORK WILL I DO,
ONCE I BECOME A MEMBER OF THE WORKING SOCIETY?
WILL YOU HAVE A LOVER? WILL YOU DEBUT AS A NOVELIST?</b>


208
00:17:33.476 --> 00:17:35.334
<b>MAY YOU LIVE A WONDERFUL LIFE.</b>

209
00:17:44.765 --> 00:17:46.493
<b>Who wants to get
a second batch of drinks?</b>


210
00:17:46.543 --> 00:17:47.911
<b>Here!</b>

211
00:17:48.461 --> 00:17:50.499
<b>Alright, all of you, come this way!</b>

212
00:17:57.602 --> 00:17:58.850
<b>Manabe.</b>

213
00:17:59.929 --> 00:18:02.407
<b>Everyone's going for a second drink.</b>

214
00:18:15.684 --> 00:18:17.492
<b>Are you okay?</b>

215
00:18:17.542 --> 00:18:19.080
<b>Water.</b>

216
00:18:38.760 --> 00:18:41.298
<b>It's been a while
since I last mingled with people.</b>


217
00:18:42.337 --> 00:18:45.803
<b>I'm so nervous that I can't even drink.</b>

218
00:18:48.970 --> 00:18:51.558
<b>You must be thinking,
why did I even come, right?</b>


219
00:19:06.882 --> 00:19:08.611
<b>Takabayashi, you…</b>

220
00:19:10.818 --> 00:19:13.296
<b>I think you don't remember me at all.</b>

221
00:19:13.885 --> 00:19:14.904
<b>What?</b>

222
00:19:16.543 --> 00:19:18.451
<b>That's not true.</b>

223
00:19:19.879 --> 00:19:21.757
<b>In sophomore year…</b>

224
00:19:23.895 --> 00:19:26.283
<b>my school uniform button fell off…</b>

225
00:19:26.812 --> 00:19:30.579
<b>and when you fixed it for me,
I was so happy.</b>


226
00:19:36.203 --> 00:19:37.961
<b>I think that did happen.</b>

227
00:19:39.809 --> 00:19:42.936
<b>You really don't remember, do you?</b>

228
00:19:44.075 --> 00:19:45.124
<b>Yeah.</b>

229
00:19:45.514 --> 00:19:46.663
<b>I'm sorry.</b>

230
00:19:49.400 --> 00:19:51.987
<b>Hey, let's get going!</b>

231
00:19:52.467 --> 00:19:55.204
<b>Stop flirting over there already.</b>

232
00:19:59.919 --> 00:20:02.497
<b>Everyone really grew into adults.</b>

233
00:20:11.488 --> 00:20:13.416
<b>It was so much fun.</b>

234
00:20:22.147 --> 00:20:24.115
<b>I had fun today.</b>

235
00:20:27.162 --> 00:20:28.700
<b>See you.</b>

236
00:21:14.684 --> 00:21:15.863
<b>This one, right?</b>

237
00:21:15.933 --> 00:21:19.380
<b>I want to put this here,
then the yellow ones in front.</b>


238
00:21:23.775 --> 00:21:26.842
<b>Wait.
What's with that get-up, Matsuri?</b>


239
00:21:27.192 --> 00:21:28.451
<b>Job interview.</b>

240
00:21:30.748 --> 00:21:33.266
<b>Something happened at the class reunion?</b>

241
00:21:34.634 --> 00:21:36.323
<b>Nothing really.</b>

242
00:21:36.922 --> 00:21:39.160
<b>I might die of boredom.</b>

243
00:21:40.009 --> 00:21:41.458
<b>Matsuri.</b>

244
00:21:42.277 --> 00:21:45.414
<b>You shouldn't mention words like "die"
in-front of those two.</b>


245
00:21:46.313 --> 00:21:47.352
<b>I know.</b>

246
00:21:49.909 --> 00:21:53.456
<b>You don't have to be in a rush.
Go at your own pace.</b>


247
00:21:55.853 --> 00:21:58.271
<b>- I'm off.
- Be well.</b>


248
00:22:01.528 --> 00:22:02.816
<b>Let's see.</b>

249
00:22:02.956 --> 00:22:05.983
<b>You dropped out of college
during your third year, correct?</b>


250
00:22:06.453 --> 00:22:07.571
<b>Yes.</b>

251
00:22:07.721 --> 00:22:10.469
<b>Any part-time experiences?</b>

252
00:22:11.388 --> 00:22:12.786
<b>I don't have one.</b>

253
00:22:13.356 --> 00:22:14.574
<b>I see.</b>

254
00:22:16.622 --> 00:22:18.540
<b>By the way,</b>

255
00:22:19.040 --> 00:22:20.878
<b>about your illness.</b>

256
00:22:21.038 --> 00:22:22.866
<b>Are you already cured?</b>

257
00:22:26.083 --> 00:22:27.252
<b>Well…</b>

258
00:23:39.499 --> 00:23:40.718
<b>Hello?</b>

259
00:23:49.469 --> 00:23:50.918
<b>Hey, Matsuri!</b>

260
00:23:51.238 --> 00:23:54.205
<b>Sorry for being late.
There was heavy traffic.</b>


261
00:23:54.834 --> 00:23:58.450
<b>But seriously, you being here
really saved my ass!</b>


262
00:23:59.999 --> 00:24:01.118
<b>What happened?</b>

263
00:24:02.077 --> 00:24:03.116
<b>Well…</b>

264
00:24:04.444 --> 00:24:06.622
<b>I don't get it myself, too.</b>

265
00:24:09.100 --> 00:24:10.359
<b>He just kinda…</b>

266
00:24:10.968 --> 00:24:12.986
<b>jumped out from his</b>

267
00:24:13.785 --> 00:24:14.824
<b>room's balcony.</b>

268
00:24:16.972 --> 00:24:19.120
<b>He's not in a critical state, though.</b>

269
00:24:19.280 --> 00:24:22.357
<b>I got a call from his parents
to come over to the hospital.</b>


270
00:24:23.236 --> 00:24:24.185
<b>No…</b>

271
00:24:24.924 --> 00:24:27.891
<b>His parents should be
the one to come here!</b>

272
00:24:44.914 --> 00:24:46.063
<b>Why are you…</b>

273
00:24:47.322 --> 00:24:49.240
<b>I got a call
from your parents.</b>


274
00:24:52.037 --> 00:24:53.935
<b>What happened to you?!</b>

275
00:24:58.321 --> 00:24:59.659
<b>I see.</b>

276
00:25:01.278 --> 00:25:02.736
<b>Sorry you had to come here.</b>

277
00:25:03.945 --> 00:25:05.643
<b>You too, Takabayashi.</b>

278
00:25:12.396 --> 00:25:13.695
<b>Seriously.</b>

279
00:25:16.412 --> 00:25:18.460
<b>Did you get into an argument
with your parents?</b>


280
00:25:20.019 --> 00:25:21.577
<b>Naturally,
they should be here!</b>


281
00:25:24.175 --> 00:25:26.752
<b>If they were ordinary parents, I guess.</b>

282
00:25:28.021 --> 00:25:29.090
<b>What?!</b>

283
00:25:30.558 --> 00:25:32.536
<b>They want to
cut ties with me, though.</b>


284
00:25:34.824 --> 00:25:37.501
<b>If I died, it's just
as they wanted it to be.</b>

285
00:25:38.590 --> 00:25:40.169
<b>That's the reason?</b>

286
00:25:41.987 --> 00:25:44.055
<b>Don't know what came over me.</b>

287
00:25:46.722 --> 00:25:47.811
<b>Hey!</b>

288
00:25:50.718 --> 00:25:51.957
<b>Is it about work?</b>

289
00:25:55.134 --> 00:25:57.292
<b>I got fired last month.</b>

290
00:25:59.030 --> 00:26:00.229
<b>No.</b>

291
00:26:00.998 --> 00:26:03.525
<b>- But that's just---
- I had so much fun.</b>


292
00:26:08.600 --> 00:26:11.747
<b>It's been a while
since I last saw everyone.</b>

293
00:26:13.056 --> 00:26:16.332
<b>Everyone's just living their own lives
just as they could.</b>


294
00:26:17.841 --> 00:26:19.939
<b>Aside from me.</b>

295
00:26:21.337 --> 00:26:23.206
<b>What are you talking about?</b>

296
00:26:26.223 --> 00:26:28.131
<b>In my time capsule…</b>

297
00:26:30.388 --> 00:26:35.753
<b>I wrote, "Please live a good life,
once you become an adult."</b>


298
00:26:38.710 --> 00:26:40.458
<b>Seems so stupid, right?</b>

299
00:26:42.886 --> 00:26:47.661
<b>I came to Tokyo without permission because
I didn't want to be controlled by my parents.</b>


300
00:26:49.809 --> 00:26:52.676
<b>I don't even know my purpose in life.</b>

301
00:26:53.925 --> 00:26:57.421
<b>When I thought about how these days
might keep dragging on longer…</b>


302
00:26:58.560 --> 00:27:00.928
<b>it just came rushing out.</b>

303
00:27:02.356 --> 00:27:05.064
<b>What do you even mean by that?</b>

304
00:27:07.551 --> 00:27:09.469
<b>- Matsuri?
- I'm sorry.</b>


305
00:27:09.629 --> 00:27:10.828
<b>I need to go.</b>

306
00:27:12.117 --> 00:27:13.745
<b>Why?
What happened?</b>


307
00:27:20.958 --> 00:27:23.495
<b>I may not know
much about you, Manabe…</b>


308
00:27:25.483 --> 00:27:27.491
<b>but that's so unfair of you.</b>

309
00:27:29.309 --> 00:27:30.728
<b>Be well.</b>

310
00:28:36.702 --> 00:28:38.410
<b>Ms. Takabayashi!</b>

311
00:28:49.319 --> 00:28:52.336
<b>You may proceed to the clinic upstairs.</b>

312
00:28:58.870 --> 00:29:00.538
<b>You're in good condition.</b>

313
00:29:00.998 --> 00:29:03.325
<b>We'll maintain your medicine dosage.</b>

314
00:29:03.895 --> 00:29:07.291
<b>Please continue to control your salt intake
and avoid strenuous exercise.</b>


315
00:29:08.270 --> 00:29:09.249
<b>Alright.</b>

316
00:29:10.878 --> 00:29:12.097
<b>How has it been?</b>

317
00:29:12.206 --> 00:29:13.705
<b>How's life at home?</b>

318
00:29:15.433 --> 00:29:17.121
<b>I've got too much free time.</b>

319
00:29:17.421 --> 00:29:19.050
<b>I can't even work.</b>

320
00:29:19.809 --> 00:29:23.585
<b>It made me feel about how this will
keep dragging on for how many years.</b>


321
00:29:25.183 --> 00:29:26.412
<b>Matsuri.</b>

322
00:29:27.042 --> 00:29:29.829
<b>I know you have looked up
a lot of information about this disease,</b>


323
00:29:29.969 --> 00:29:32.286
<b>but anything is possible
with this disease.</b>


324
00:29:33.145 --> 00:29:35.293
<b>Medical standards are also improving,</b>

325
00:29:35.733 --> 00:29:37.501
<b>so let's both do our best!</b>

326
00:29:39.649 --> 00:29:42.906
<b>I'm looking forward to the day
you create that special medicine soon.</b>


327
00:29:45.603 --> 00:29:46.832
<b>Of course.</b>

328
00:29:47.121 --> 00:29:48.540
<b>I'll do my best.</b>

329
00:29:53.795 --> 00:29:55.373
<b>Mail for you.</b>

330
00:29:55.553 --> 00:29:58.021
<b>Wasn't this from your
class reunion last time?</b>


331
00:29:58.140 --> 00:29:59.169
<b>What?</b>

332
00:30:03.235 --> 00:30:04.584
<b>Let me see.</b>

333
00:30:05.523 --> 00:30:07.331
<b>Oh, my.</b>

334
00:30:11.517 --> 00:30:13.425
<b>Is this Miyuki?</b>

335
00:30:13.795 --> 00:30:16.632
<b>She looks like a completely different person!</b>

336
00:30:18.550 --> 00:30:21.127
<b>Everyone's grown into adults.</b>

337
00:30:36.782 --> 00:30:37.871
<b>Yes?</b>

338
00:30:40.318 --> 00:30:42.276
<b><i>It's me, 
Manabe.</i></b>

339
00:30:42.916 --> 00:30:43.955
<b>What?</b>

340
00:30:44.594 --> 00:30:47.141
<b><i>Well, I… I just…</i></b>

341
00:30:47.601 --> 00:30:51.497
<b><i>I got discharged last week, and was
wondering if we could talk for a while?</i></b>


342
00:30:51.687 --> 00:30:54.284
<b><i>Let's celebrate!
I'll send the address to you.</i></b>


343
00:30:54.364 --> 00:30:56.442
<b><i>I just sent it.
All good?</i></b>


344
00:30:56.492 --> 00:30:59.499
<b><i>- Okay? Alright, hanging up. I sent it.</i>
- Hey, wait. No, wait.</b>


345
00:31:04.494 --> 00:31:08.070
<b>Every time I come here,
I keep eating everything.</b>


346
00:31:08.220 --> 00:31:11.867
<b>So many original dishes,
and "Gen's Special" is specially good!</b>


347
00:31:12.626 --> 00:31:13.985
<b>Thanks for the wait!</b>

348
00:31:14.694 --> 00:31:17.990
<b>Mr. Gen!
These are my classmates from middle-school.</b>


349
00:31:19.139 --> 00:31:20.498
<b>Welcome.</b>

350
00:31:21.347 --> 00:31:24.194
<b>Mr. Gen is like
my father here in Tokyo.</b>

351
00:31:24.324 --> 00:31:27.191
<b>I always come to him for advices!</b>

352
00:31:27.651 --> 00:31:29.249
<b>Enjoy your time.</b>

353
00:31:29.959 --> 00:31:30.958
<b>Yes.</b>

354
00:31:31.917 --> 00:31:34.874
<b>Alright, now that everybody's here,
let's drink to that.</b>


355
00:31:36.382 --> 00:31:37.461
<b>Alright.</b>

356
00:31:38.300 --> 00:31:40.878
<b>Congrats on getting discharged!</b>

357
00:31:40.977 --> 00:31:42.916
<b>Cheers!</b>

358
00:31:50.598 --> 00:31:52.136
<b>You know what?</b>

359
00:31:52.896 --> 00:31:55.923
<b>We'll listen to what you have to say,
no matter what. Right, Matsuri?</b>


360
00:31:56.122 --> 00:31:57.201
<b>Why me?</b>

361
00:31:57.841 --> 00:32:01.117
<b>Well you know,
the mood kinda turned weird last time.</b>


362
00:32:01.667 --> 00:32:04.244
<b>Kazu here wants to say something.</b>

363
00:32:06.132 --> 00:32:07.081
<b>Go ahead.</b>

364
00:32:19.709 --> 00:32:21.387
<b>What? Am I interfering?</b>

365
00:32:21.487 --> 00:32:22.666
<b>No.</b>

366
00:32:23.915 --> 00:32:25.443
<b>I just need a moment.
Sorry about that.</b>


367
00:32:25.563 --> 00:32:27.051
<b>- Yeah.
- My bad.</b>


368
00:32:28.030 --> 00:32:30.238
<b>Yeah, yeah. I got it.</b>

369
00:32:38.070 --> 00:32:40.008
<b>About that other day…</b>

370
00:32:40.598 --> 00:32:41.966
<b>I'm sorry.</b>

371
00:32:43.365 --> 00:32:44.654
<b>No…</b>

372
00:32:44.913 --> 00:32:47.121
<b>I owe you an apology, too.</b>

373
00:32:48.230 --> 00:32:50.378
<b>Congrats on your discharge.</b>

374
00:32:52.985 --> 00:32:54.794
<b>Well, it's just…</b>

375
00:32:59.509 --> 00:33:00.957
<b>I…</b>

376
00:33:02.216 --> 00:33:03.325
<b>I saw you.</b>

377
00:33:07.801 --> 00:33:09.589
<b>Is she sick?</b>

378
00:33:14.993 --> 00:33:15.992
<b>Your mom?</b>

379
00:33:17.741 --> 00:33:18.700
<b>What?</b>

380
00:33:28.060 --> 00:33:32.266
<b>I've been thinking about
what you said this whole time.</b>


381
00:33:33.045 --> 00:33:34.154
<b>Well…</b>

382
00:33:34.544 --> 00:33:36.452
<b>when you said
I was being unfair.</b>


383
00:33:37.081 --> 00:33:39.739
<b>Even when there's people out there
who wants to live, but can't,</b>


384
00:33:39.878 --> 00:33:42.895
<b>and I wasn't thinking about how
you felt about it.</b>


385
00:33:43.275 --> 00:33:45.333
<b>I said a bunch of childish stuff.</b>

386
00:33:45.703 --> 00:33:47.281
<b>I'm really…</b>

387
00:33:47.840 --> 00:33:49.139
<b>really sorry.</b>

388
00:33:58.770 --> 00:34:01.437
<b>Can you not kill off my mom one-sidedly?</b>

389
00:34:01.836 --> 00:34:04.534
<b>No, I'm sorry. 
I didn't mean it that way.</b>

390
00:34:05.753 --> 00:34:08.040
<b>What did you mean, then?</b>

391
00:34:08.200 --> 00:34:09.789
<b>Well, as I said…</b>

392
00:34:11.577 --> 00:34:12.955
<b>How do I say this…?</b>

393
00:34:13.005 --> 00:34:15.663
<b>- Hey, Takeru.
- Hey, you done?</b>


394
00:34:16.062 --> 00:34:18.680
<b>Manabe killed my mom.</b>

395
00:34:19.269 --> 00:34:22.915
<b>- What? Really?
- No, no. That's not what I meant!</b>


396
00:34:22.965 --> 00:34:25.513
<b>- What happened?
- Explain it well.</b>


397
00:34:25.653 --> 00:34:28.180
<b>- What were you talking about?
- I was joking.</b>


398
00:34:28.510 --> 00:34:29.958
<b>- So? What?
- Well…</b>


399
00:34:30.058 --> 00:34:32.536
<b>We should come together again soon!</b>

400
00:34:32.636 --> 00:34:34.883
<b>Hey, Kazu!
Make sure you take her home!</b>


401
00:34:34.963 --> 00:34:36.941
<b>- I know.
- Got that?</b>


402
00:34:37.081 --> 00:34:39.399
<b>- We can go now.
- See you.</b>


403
00:34:39.489 --> 00:34:40.658
<b>- Bye-bye!
- See you.</b>


404
00:34:51.357 --> 00:34:53.305
<b>Sorry, it's my dad.</b>

405
00:34:56.342 --> 00:34:57.551
<b>Yes?</b>

406
00:34:59.039 --> 00:35:00.498
<b>On my way home now.</b>

407
00:35:01.886 --> 00:35:04.094
<b>It's okay, I can go back by myself.</b>

408
00:35:06.172 --> 00:35:07.311
<b>Yeah.</b>

409
00:35:13.335 --> 00:35:15.543
<b>You seem very close with your family.</b>

410
00:35:16.562 --> 00:35:18.210
<b>They're too overprotective.</b>

411
00:35:19.149 --> 00:35:21.577
<b>I'm already an adult, though.</b>

412
00:35:29.179 --> 00:35:30.827
<b>So pretty.</b>

413
00:35:41.467 --> 00:35:43.784
<b>Why do you have that?</b>

414
00:35:47.950 --> 00:35:51.577
<b>When I see something nice,
I want to leave a memory of it.</b>


415
00:35:53.245 --> 00:35:54.664
<b>Really?</b>

416
00:35:55.952 --> 00:35:57.371
<b>Kinda nice.</b>

417
00:36:02.076 --> 00:36:04.234
<b>What are you gonna do from now on?</b>

418
00:36:04.654 --> 00:36:06.482
<b>Why the sudden question?</b>

419
00:36:06.682 --> 00:36:08.160
<b>From now on?</b>

420
00:36:08.709 --> 00:36:09.669
<b>Well…</b>

421
00:36:09.758 --> 00:36:11.557
<b>I'm not sure.</b>

422
00:36:13.694 --> 00:36:15.623
<b>For now…</b>

423
00:36:17.121 --> 00:36:19.269
<b>gotta find a job…</b>

424
00:36:20.038 --> 00:36:23.035
<b>- and pay my rent.
- What's with that?</b>


425
00:36:23.884 --> 00:36:26.042
<b>You must have something else.</b>

426
00:36:26.632 --> 00:36:29.499
<b>Something else? 
What else?</b>

427
00:36:33.375 --> 00:36:35.043
<b>Let's see…</b>

428
00:36:38.000 --> 00:36:39.579
<b>What about…?</b>

429
00:36:40.518 --> 00:36:41.916
<b>Then…</b>

430
00:36:44.564 --> 00:36:46.661
<b>I'll do my best, too.</b>

431
00:36:50.358 --> 00:36:53.375
<b>So please don't ever think again
about wanting to die.</b>


432
00:37:00.288 --> 00:37:01.577
<b>You got it.</b>

433
00:37:43.125 --> 00:37:44.623
<b>That startled me!</b>

434
00:37:56.831 --> 00:37:58.330
<b><i>You got it.</i></b>

435
00:38:07.251 --> 00:38:10.488
<b>What? Really? 
Is that guy okay now?</b>

436
00:38:10.627 --> 00:38:11.616
<b>I wonder.</b>

437
00:38:16.831 --> 00:38:18.040
<b>Over here.</b>

438
00:38:20.428 --> 00:38:22.436
<b>It surprised me a bit.</b>

439
00:38:22.725 --> 00:38:25.912
<b>If I were you,
I'd be fuming mad at him.</b>


440
00:38:27.940 --> 00:38:28.989
<b>Well…</b>

441
00:38:29.119 --> 00:38:32.116
<b>I can kinda understand
where he's coming from.</b>


442
00:38:32.745 --> 00:38:35.163
<b>Like, wanting to run away from something.</b>

443
00:38:37.001 --> 00:38:39.578
<b>Anyway, as my senior at work,</b>

444
00:38:39.788 --> 00:38:42.036
<b>I might as well
let you look over me.</b>

445
00:38:42.086 --> 00:38:44.414
<b>But Matsuri, starting today…</b>

446
00:38:45.453 --> 00:38:48.020
<b>I love you, Sanae!</b>

447
00:38:48.130 --> 00:38:49.998
<b>Thank you!</b>

448
00:38:50.807 --> 00:38:53.325
<b>You gotta introduce me to
some hottie, got that?</b>


449
00:38:57.131 --> 00:38:58.949
<b>The Editor-in-Chief is here.
Let's go.</b>


450
