00:41:07.410 --> 00:41:08.789
<b>Yeah, my bad.</b>

482
00:41:11.187 --> 00:41:12.455
<b>Well…</b>

483
00:41:13.105 --> 00:41:14.244
<b>I…</b>

484
00:41:15.213 --> 00:41:18.040
<b>I've been thinking
of a lot of things since that day…</b>


485
00:41:19.788 --> 00:41:21.207
