527
00:46:42.385 --> 00:46:44.203
<b>They said…</b>

528
00:46:45.242 --> 00:46:47.051
<b>she's got 3-4 years left.</b>

529
00:46:47.720 --> 00:46:48.849
<b>What?</b>

530
00:46:49.058 --> 00:46:50.757
<b>Is that so?</b>

531
00:46:51.406 --> 00:46:54.293
<b>Really? What a pity.</b>

532
00:46:55.013 --> 00:46:57.420
<b>Seeing your child die before you.</b>

533
00:46:59.009 --> 00:47:01.306
<b>She's still so young.</b>

534
00:47:03.864 --> 00:47:05.322
<b>- Crap.
- I'm so hungry!</b>


535
00:47:05.362 --> 00:47:06.551
<b>Crap!</b>

536
00:47:09.088 --> 00:47:11.796
<b>You're going independent?! Why?</b>

537
00:47:12.875 --> 00:47:15.372
<b>It's not like it's gonna happen immediately,</b>

538
00:47:15.622 --> 00:47:17.570
<b>but I'd like to learn the ropes.</b>

539
00:47:17.710 --> 00:47:20.787
<b>It might take about
3-4 years, Mr. Gen said.</b>

540
00:47:23.054 --> 00:47:24.263
<b>But…</b>

541
00:47:24.773 --> 00:47:26.091
<b>I'm still worried about it.</b>

542
00:47:26.221 --> 00:47:27.560
<b>- Why?!
- Why?!</b>


543
00:47:30.417 --> 00:47:31.706
<b>But why?</b>

544
00:47:36.301 --> 00:47:39.258
<b>I'm having fun now, though…</b>

545
00:47:40.537 --> 00:47:43.964
<b>So I thought, it'd be good
if these days could just go on…</b>


546
00:47:44.153 --> 00:47:47.580
<b>That part of you is just not it.</b>

547
00:47:48.339 --> 00:47:51.936
<b>Well… I mean, it's also your good side.</b>

548
00:47:52.715 --> 00:47:54.523
<b>- Thank you.
- Thanks for having us.</b>


549
00:47:54.653 --> 00:47:57.070
<b>- I'll reach out to you soon.
- Yeah, see you.</b>


550
00:47:58.119 --> 00:47:59.758
<b>You need to decide today.</b>

551
00:48:00.037 --> 00:48:02.175
<b>- Come on, we're leaving.
- Yeah. Yeah.</b>


552
00:48:02.415 --> 00:48:03.764
<b>Goodnight.</b>

553
00:48:03.964 --> 00:48:06.411
<b>Take care, you two. See you.</b>

554
00:48:07.090 --> 00:48:08.329
<b>Thanks!</b>

555
00:48:22.245 --> 00:48:23.864
<b>It's fine, I'll do that.</b>

556
00:48:24.193 --> 00:48:25.482
<b>I'm good.</b>

557
00:48:27.930 --> 00:48:29.888
<b>Takeru and Sanae would look perfect</b>

558
00:48:30.047 --> 00:48:32.455
<b>as a married couple, huh?</b>

559
00:48:34.293 --> 00:48:35.652
<b>Right.</b>

560
00:48:36.031 --> 00:48:38.029
<b>I thought, they suit each other.</b>

561
00:48:52.775 --> 00:48:53.904
<b>And…</b>

562
00:48:54.513 --> 00:48:56.161
<b>everything's
all thanks to you.</b>


563
00:49:03.324 --> 00:49:04.453
<b>Thank you.</b>

564
00:49:08.199 --> 00:49:09.838
<b>Suddenly bringing that up.</b>

565
00:49:10.267 --> 00:49:11.496
<b>You're scaring me.</b>

566
00:49:36.641 --> 00:49:38.659
<b>I'll be straight with you.</b>

567
00:49:39.578 --> 00:49:42.755
<b>Who do you see me as?</b>

568
00:49:47.530 --> 00:49:48.869
<b>How do I see you?</b>

569
00:49:53.384 --> 00:49:54.922
<b>I don't know.</b>

570
00:50:21.516 --> 00:50:22.864
<b>I'm in the middle
of cleaning up.</b>


571
00:51:29.118 --> 00:51:31.176
<b>Sorry. I need to go.</b>

572
00:53:22.814 --> 00:53:24.742
<b>Should we try changing your medication?</b>

573
00:53:24.872 --> 00:53:27.100
<b>We'll increase Furosemide to 80 mg,</b>

574
00:53:27.210 --> 00:53:29.448
<b>and add a new medicine with it.</b>

575
00:53:32.894 --> 00:53:34.483
<b>No need to get worried.</b>

576
00:53:34.652 --> 00:53:37.640
<b>Taking the same drug for a long time
will produce drug immunity,</b>


577
00:53:37.779 --> 00:53:40.557
<b>so it'll be better
to make a few adjustments.</b>


578
00:53:43.014 --> 00:53:45.582
<b>This new medicine will surely…</b>

579
00:54:16.041 --> 00:54:21.685
<b>TEXT FROM KAZU:
I WANT TO TALK TO YOU.
CAN WE MEET TOMORROW?</b>


580
00:54:35.681 --> 00:54:37.000
<b>The other day…</b>

581
00:54:37.580 --> 00:54:39.657
<b>I'm sorry if the mood turned sour.</b>

582
00:54:44.792 --> 00:54:47.220
<b>But I really want to know.</b>

583
00:54:49.168 --> 00:54:51.206
<b>I'm good with the way things are.</b>

584
00:54:52.075 --> 00:54:54.163
<b>You said it yourself before.</b>

585
00:54:54.563 --> 00:54:56.411
<b>That you prefer the way things are now.</b>

586
00:54:56.730 --> 00:54:59.208
<b>Well, that and this
have different meanings.</b>


587
00:54:59.278 --> 00:55:01.506
<b>Based on what you think.</b>

588
00:55:02.964 --> 00:55:05.052
<b>No, wait, wait.</b>

589
00:55:07.040 --> 00:55:09.897
<b>Did I do something that upset you?</b>

590
00:55:10.576 --> 00:55:12.515
<b>I'm not upset, though.</b>

591
00:55:12.934 --> 00:55:15.372
<b>But it's weird
how you've been acting this way.</b>


592
00:55:16.590 --> 00:55:19.248
<b>If you don't see me as a man,
then just say that.</b>


593
00:55:22.365 --> 00:55:23.693
<b>I…</b>

594
00:55:24.652 --> 00:55:26.660
<b>I like you, Matsuri.</b>

595
00:55:28.948 --> 00:55:30.666
<b>I want to be with you.</b>

596
00:55:32.714 --> 00:55:34.073
<b>Just for now.</b>

597
00:55:36.221 --> 00:55:36.950
<b>What?</b>

598
00:55:37.679 --> 00:55:41.885
<b>You feel fully satisfied right now 
and because you feel comfortable with me, 
that's why you want to be with me---</b>


599
00:55:41.945 --> 00:55:45.062
<b>Now, why would reach that conclusion?!
There's no way that's true!</b>


600
00:55:47.450 --> 00:55:49.068
<b>Just to tell you…</b>

601
00:55:50.646 --> 00:55:54.562
<b>I know one day, you'll regret
having met someone weird like me.</b>


602
00:55:54.612 --> 00:55:56.700
<b>If you thought about it naturally,
there's just no way.</b>


603
00:55:56.800 --> 00:55:58.329
<b>What do you mean,
"naturally"?</b>


604
00:55:58.399 --> 00:56:01.206
<b>As I said, what's natural is natural.</b>

605
00:56:01.386 --> 00:56:03.014
<b>You know nothing about me.</b>

606
00:56:03.094 --> 00:56:05.551
<b>Can you not decide everything for me?!</b>

607
00:56:15.671 --> 00:56:17.649
<b>Matsuri, are you okay?</b>

608
00:56:18.079 --> 00:56:19.038
<b>Sorry.</b>

609
00:56:22.514 --> 00:56:24.792
<b>Hey, wait. Wait.</b>

610
00:56:25.551 --> 00:56:26.840
<b>Matsuri.</b>

611
00:56:27.270 --> 00:56:29.847
<b>Matsuri. What's wrong?</b>

612
00:56:30.417 --> 00:56:31.396
<b>Matsuri?</b>

613
00:56:33.673 --> 00:56:34.912
<b>Matsuri?</b>

614
00:56:35.172 --> 00:56:36.411
<b>Matsuri?</b>

615
00:56:36.680 --> 00:56:39.228
<b>What
-What's wrong? Matsuri?</b>

616
00:56:39.358 --> 00:56:40.646
<b>Matsuri!</b>

617
00:57:20.706 --> 00:57:21.785
<b>Matsuri.</b>

618
00:57:24.373 --> 00:57:25.661
<b>Kazu…</b>

619
00:57:28.518 --> 00:57:29.857
<b>Are you okay?</b>

620
00:57:31.975 --> 00:57:33.613
<b>You're exaggerating.</b>

621
00:57:34.622 --> 00:57:36.790
<b>I'm just anemic.</b>

622
00:57:42.005 --> 00:57:43.843
<b>Your father told me.</b>

623
00:57:47.469 --> 00:57:50.367
<b>"I hope you can accept
everything about Matsuri."</b>


624
00:57:54.103 --> 00:57:55.332
<b>Tell me.</b>

625
00:58:06.570 --> 00:58:09.747
<b>I got a respiratory organ disease
when I was 20 years old.</b>


626
00:58:15.811 --> 00:58:17.829
<b>I had a surgery.</b>

627
00:58:21.405 --> 00:58:23.923
<b>I still have scars due to that.</b>

628
00:58:25.132 --> 00:58:27.849
<b>It may trigger asthma…</b>

629
00:58:28.998 --> 00:58:31.565
<b>and I'm not allowed to do
any strenuous activity.</b>


630
00:58:36.111 --> 00:58:37.609
<b>Sorry.</b>

631
00:58:39.068 --> 00:58:41.465
<b>I was acting so self-righteous to you,</b>

632
00:58:41.725 --> 00:58:43.523
<b>when I'm in such a state.</b>

633
00:58:45.052 --> 00:58:46.760
<b>Funny, right?</b>

634
00:58:48.179 --> 00:58:49.697
<b>That's not true.</b>

635
00:58:51.565 --> 00:58:53.623
<b>You just gotta rest well for now.</b>

636
00:58:57.579 --> 00:58:58.938
<b>No.</b>

637
00:59:04.223 --> 00:59:05.282
<b>I…</b>

638
00:59:05.881 --> 00:59:08.818
<b>I'm not the kind of person
you thought me to be.</b>


639
00:59:20.876 --> 00:59:23.094
<b>Don't come here anymore.</b>

640
00:59:30.696 --> 00:59:32.464
<b>I don't want to see you.</b>

641
01:00:12.624 --> 01:00:14.352
<b>I'm going now.</b>

642
01:00:15.182 --> 01:00:16.530
<b>Where are you going?</b>

643
01:00:16.610 --> 01:00:18.039
<b>Just somewhere.</b>

644
01:00:18.109 --> 01:00:20.177
<b>You just got discharged.
Will you be alright?</b>


645
01:00:20.246 --> 01:00:22.294
<b>I'll be fine. 
You worry too much.</b>

646
01:00:22.404 --> 01:00:23.533
<b>Matsuri.</b>

647
01:00:25.241 --> 01:00:26.760
<b>You have a moment?</b>

648
01:00:27.030 --> 01:00:28.368
<b>What's wrong?</b>

649
01:00:28.938 --> 01:00:31.655
<b>Something I need to
consult with you about. You too, dad.</b>


650
01:00:42.065 --> 01:00:43.563
<b>This hospital.</b>

651
01:00:44.183 --> 01:00:45.891
