652
01:00:45.951 --> 01:00:48.558
<b>A special unit was just recently established.</b>

653
01:00:51.845 --> 01:00:52.814
<b>I…</b>

654
01:00:53.753 --> 01:00:57.229
<b>We were thinking of consulting
Dr. Hirata about it,</b>


655
01:00:57.579 --> 01:01:00.576
<b>to see if we can
transfer you to a different hospital.</b>


656
01:01:05.881 --> 01:01:07.739
<b>What do you think, Matsuri?</b>

657
01:01:10.506 --> 01:01:12.884
<b>My body can't be cured from
this disease anyway.</b>


658
01:01:13.054 --> 01:01:15.321
<b>We've tried a lot already, haven't we?</b>

659
01:01:15.821 --> 01:01:17.699
<b>That might true…</b>

660
01:01:18.538 --> 01:01:19.357
<b>But…</b>

661
01:01:20.556 --> 01:01:22.944
<b>medicines are always advancing.</b>

662
01:01:23.263 --> 01:01:25.701
<b>The situation might also slowly change.</b>

663
01:01:26.151 --> 01:01:27.399
<b>You know?</b>

664
01:01:27.489 --> 01:01:31.625
<b>Once you feel like it, we can always
go and see the Doctor anytime.</b>


665
01:01:32.035 --> 01:01:34.582
<b>- There's a possibility--
- Give it up.</b>


666
01:01:38.748 --> 01:01:41.215
<b>No matter how difficult it is
to cure this disease,</b>


667
01:01:41.485 --> 01:01:44.782
<b>if there's any way to cure it at all,
