668
01:01:45.771 --> 01:01:47.619
<b>But this disease
doesn't have that.</b>


669
01:01:52.075 --> 01:01:55.012
<b>It's not that I've given up on fighting.</b>

670
01:01:56.960 --> 01:01:59.197
<b>I just can no longer fight back.</b>

671
01:02:02.504 --> 01:02:03.813
<b>Matsuri.</b>

