01:19:26.139 --> 01:19:27.039
<b>Thank you.</b>

885
01:19:28.267 --> 01:19:30.405
<b>I deeply appreciate the thought.</b>

886
01:19:36.589 --> 01:19:39.986
<b>If I can help someone
who has the same disease as me…</b>


887
01:19:41.474 --> 01:19:43.282
<b>even that alone,</b>

888
01:19:44.481 --> 01:19:48.687
<b>would feel like there was
a purpose for my existence.</b>


889
01:19:52.583 --> 01:19:53.832
<b>Matsuri…</b>

890
01:20:01.264 --> 01:20:04.351
<b>There's one last thing I need to do.</b>

891
01:20:06.739 --> 01:20:09.426
<b>Once it's done, 
I'll come see you again, okay?</b>

892
01:20:33.722 --> 01:20:34.921
<b>Down there.</b>

893
01:20:50.155 --> 01:20:51.834
<b>You're not gonna slide down?</b>

894
01:20:52.373 --> 01:20:54.821
<b>I'd die. I'm sick, remember?</b>

895
01:20:56.009 --> 01:20:57.488
<b>Then, you know…</b>

896
01:20:58.617 --> 01:21:00.125
<b>Wanna try that out?</b>

897
01:21:03.012 --> 01:21:06.029
<b>- It's embarrassing! I'd be too embarrassed!
- No, come on. Come here.</b>


898
01:21:09.526 --> 01:21:11.514
<b>It's moving fast!</b>

899
01:21:11.834 --> 01:21:14.321
<b>Wait, wait. Turn!</b>

900
01:21:17.718 --> 01:21:18.787
<b>Oh, crap!</b>

901
01:21:24.971 --> 01:21:27.388
<b>- Are you okay?
- I'm good!</b>


902
01:21:27.588 --> 01:21:28.937
<b>What a relief.</b>

903
01:21:36.069 --> 01:21:37.818
<b>That was scary!</b>

904
01:22:10.895 --> 01:22:13.542
<b>I wanted to give this to you
at a time where I look charming, but…</b>


905
01:22:24.081 --> 01:22:25.250
<b>You know?</b>

906
01:22:28.887 --> 01:22:30.875
<b>As long as you're with me…</b>

907
01:22:32.073 --> 01:22:34.661
<b>it makes me feel like
I can take on anything.</b>


908
01:22:38.257 --> 01:22:39.416
<b>So…</b>

909
01:22:44.950 --> 01:22:47.448
<b>Please, will you marry me?</b>

910
01:23:02.912 --> 01:23:05.370
<b>You're so lame, so no!</b>

911
01:23:07.658 --> 01:23:09.006
<b>You're kidding!</b>

912
01:23:09.186 --> 01:23:10.675
<b>No way!</b>

913
01:25:24.561 --> 01:25:26.139
<b>Matsuri!</b>

914
01:25:26.918 --> 01:25:28.107
<b>Matsuri!</b>

915
01:25:28.896 --> 01:25:30.135
<b>Wait!</b>

916
01:25:34.651 --> 01:25:35.799
<b>Why?</b>

917
01:25:37.757 --> 01:25:40.724
<b>Did I do something that upset you?</b>

918
01:25:43.552 --> 01:25:44.551
<b>No.</b>

919
01:25:47.737 --> 01:25:49.366
<b>What's wrong, then?</b>

920
01:25:52.842 --> 01:25:54.661
<b>You did nothing wrong.</b>

921
01:25:56.079 --> 01:25:57.707
<b>It's all my fault.</b>

922
01:26:10.005 --> 01:26:12.203
<b>I've been lying to you all this time.</b>

923
01:26:13.951 --> 01:26:15.080
<b>What?</b>

924
01:26:27.817 --> 01:26:30.075
<b>It's an incurable disease.</b>

925
01:26:36.589 --> 01:26:37.867
<b>So…</b>

926
01:26:40.245 --> 01:26:42.333
<b>I can no longer be with you.</b>

927
01:26:45.350 --> 01:26:47.048
<b>I'm sorry.</b>

928
01:27:01.504 --> 01:27:03.821
<b>Incurable?</b>

929
01:27:07.448 --> 01:27:09.206
<b>How about medicines or…</b>

930
01:27:09.685 --> 01:27:12.283
<b>Or if you get hospitalized for
regular treatment…</b>


931
01:27:12.393 --> 01:27:13.791
<b>It won't work.</b>

932
01:27:18.227 --> 01:27:21.034
<b>Generally, no one can live another 10 years.</b>

933
01:27:26.748 --> 01:27:28.117
<b>Goodbye.</b>

934
01:27:33.422 --> 01:27:37.947
<b>Wait. No, wait. Wait, just wait.
I'm sorry, okay?</b>


935
01:27:39.556 --> 01:27:40.924
<b>I just…</b>

936
01:27:41.494 --> 01:27:43.641
<b>My mind's in a mess and…</b>

937
01:27:46.589 --> 01:27:47.787
<b>Why?</b>

938
01:27:48.606 --> 01:27:50.455
<b>Why does it have to be you?</b>

939
01:27:52.283 --> 01:27:54.541
<b>I've been thinking about it all this time.</b>

940
01:27:56.808 --> 01:27:59.336
<b>"Why did it have to be me?"</b>

941
01:28:01.084 --> 01:28:03.352
<b>Last 10 years? 
How ridiculous.</b>

942
01:28:04.521 --> 01:28:06.748
<b>You think it's long or too short?</b>

943
01:28:07.877 --> 01:28:10.235
<b>Whichever it is, it's still my win.</b>

944
01:28:12.912 --> 01:28:15.540
<b>I thought I was
bored out of my mind.</b>

945
01:28:16.019 --> 01:28:18.477
<b>"Let me die already"…</b>

946
01:28:20.045 --> 01:28:22.183
<b>was what I used to think everyday.</b>

947
01:28:36.978 --> 01:28:38.197
<b>But…</b>

948
01:28:44.041 --> 01:28:46.199
<b>since I met you…</b>

949
01:28:48.846 --> 01:28:50.944
<b>every day has been so much fun.</b>

950
01:28:56.439 --> 01:28:58.946
<b>But this is as far I can go.</b>

951
01:29:07.967 --> 01:29:10.355
<b>If I stay with you any longer…</b>

952
01:29:12.652 --> 01:29:14.790
<b>it'll make me fear death.</b>

953
01:29:21.773 --> 01:29:23.032
<b>I…</b>

954
01:29:24.900 --> 01:29:25.999
<b>I…</b>

955
01:29:28.546 --> 01:29:30.654
<b>I like you, Matsuri!</b>

956
01:29:47.617 --> 01:29:48.876
<b>Kazu?</b>

957
01:29:52.612 --> 01:29:55.310
<b>For making me your girlfriend…</b>

958
01:29:56.818 --> 01:29:58.157
<b>Thank you.</b>

959
01:30:00.105 --> 01:30:01.284
<b>No!</b>

960
01:30:02.562 --> 01:30:04.041
<b>Kazu, you…</b>

961
01:30:05.529 --> 01:30:08.117
<b>You need to get yourself together and live.</b>

962
01:30:09.006 --> 01:30:10.744
<b>I don't want it.</b>

963
01:30:13.661 --> 01:30:15.050
<b>I'm asking you.</b>

964
01:30:15.170 --> 01:30:17.657
<b>Just say you understand.</b>

965
01:30:21.354 --> 01:30:24.490
<b>I need to start preparing for death.</b>

966
01:30:27.997 --> 01:30:29.955
<b>This is my last wish.</b>

967
01:30:42.862 --> 01:30:43.991
<b>I got it.</b>

968
01:30:49.046 --> 01:30:50.245
<b>Thank you.</b>

969
01:31:23.541 --> 01:31:24.660
<b>Welcome back.</b>

970
01:31:24.760 --> 01:31:25.779
<b>I'm home.</b>

971
01:31:25.889 --> 01:31:28.746
<b>Welcome back. 
You're home early.</b>

972
01:31:57.088 --> 01:31:58.726
<b>Looks good.</b>

973
01:31:59.086 --> 01:32:01.763
<b>Dinner will be served in a while.</b>

974
01:32:02.442 --> 01:32:04.181
<b>How was the trip?</b>

975
01:32:25.050 --> 01:32:26.289
<b>Matsuri?</b>

976
01:32:31.264 --> 01:32:32.922
<b>Hey, mom?</b>

977
01:32:50.734 --> 01:32:52.033
<b>I…</b>

978
01:32:56.388 --> 01:32:58.966
<b>I want to live more.</b>

979
01:33:08.536 --> 01:33:10.205
<b>I also want…</b>

980
01:33:11.124 --> 01:33:13.152
<b>to travel a bit more.</b>

981
01:33:15.050 --> 01:33:17.507
<b>I want to go out with my friends…</b>

982
01:33:18.276 --> 01:33:19.865
<b>and be able to work…</b>

983
01:33:21.234 --> 01:33:23.821
<b>and I want to get married too…</b>

984
01:33:30.984 --> 01:33:32.772
<b>I haven't even…</b>

985
01:33:33.371 --> 01:33:36.089
<b>experienced being a mother.</b>

986
01:33:38.766 --> 01:33:41.723
<b>I'm sorry for always causing so much trouble.</b>

987
01:33:46.149 --> 01:33:47.747
<b>Matsuri…</b>

988
01:33:49.226 --> 01:33:50.704
<b>You know what?</b>

989
01:33:51.283 --> 01:33:53.112
<b>I've always regretted it.</b>

990
01:33:54.031 --> 01:33:56.978
<b>The day the Doctor
told me about your illness…</b>


991
01:33:57.347 --> 01:34:00.055
<b>we were all feeling downhearted.</b>

992
01:34:01.114 --> 01:34:03.172
<b>We started crying</b>

993
01:34:03.331 --> 01:34:04.870
<b>before you even could.</b>

994
01:34:06.558 --> 01:34:09.505
<b>That's why you've never cried
all this time, right?</b>


995
01:34:10.764 --> 01:34:12.282
<b>I'm sorry.</b>

996
01:34:16.468 --> 01:34:17.837
<b>But you know?</b>

997
01:34:20.664 --> 01:34:23.301
<b>It's totally fine if you want to…</b>

998
01:34:23.831 --> 01:34:25.539
<b>cry a little bit more,</b>

999
01:34:26.348 --> 01:34:28.596
<b>shout and rant a bit more, too.</b>

1000
01:34:31.553 --> 01:34:33.931
<b>I will accept all of that!</b>

1001
01:34:46.718 --> 01:34:48.446
<b>I don't want to die.</b>

1002
01:34:53.651 --> 01:34:55.569
<b>I don't want to die!</b>

