<b><i>The government decided to abolish the
current year name, "Heisei", starting today.</i></b>


1004
01:35:40.384 --> 01:35:42.142
<b><i>In the press conference just now,</i></b>

1005
01:35:42.262 --> 01:35:45.129
<b><i>they have introduced a new
year name, called "Reiwa".</i></b>


1006
01:35:45.309 --> 01:35:47.987
<b><i>The inauguration of a new era.</i></b>

1007
01:36:20.894 --> 01:36:22.212
<b>Sounds good?</b>

1008
01:36:23.571 --> 01:36:25.159
<b>Seems like
something you'd do.</b>


1009
01:36:28.556 --> 01:36:30.284
<b>I thought so, too.</b>

1010
01:36:32.392 --> 01:36:33.831
<b>I'll have it here.</b>

1011
01:36:44.600 --> 01:36:46.118
<b>We're almost there.</b>

1012
01:36:47.147 --> 01:36:50.954
<b>As the Editor in charge of you,
I'll surely get this out.</b>


1013
01:36:53.861 --> 01:36:55.749
<b>I'm looking forward to that.</b>

1014
01:37:02.972 --> 01:37:05.419
<b>Is Takeru doing good?</b>

1015
01:37:13.161 --> 01:37:14.700
<b>We broke up.</b>

1016
01:37:17.297 --> 01:37:18.326
<b>Why?</b>

1017
01:37:20.174 --> 01:37:22.082
<b>How do I put this…?</b>

1018
01:37:27.047 --> 01:37:29.535
<b>You know,
work has been very fulfilling so far,</b>


1019
01:37:29.905 --> 01:37:32.852
<b>and I want to put all my focus
on this book.</b>


1020
01:37:39.305 --> 01:37:40.544
<b>Sanae…</b>

1021
01:37:45.509 --> 01:37:46.997
<b>Thank you.</b>

1022
01:37:50.594 --> 01:37:51.663
<b>Not at all.</b>

1023
01:37:54.700 --> 01:37:56.258
<b>Pleasure is mine.</b>

1024
01:38:15.729 --> 01:38:17.097
<b><i>A little early, though.</i></b>

1025
01:38:18.196 --> 01:38:19.395
<b>Congrats.</b>

1026
01:38:20.474 --> 01:38:21.823
<b>Thank you.</b>

1027
01:38:31.293 --> 01:38:34.270
<b>Remember the first day you arrived here?</b>

1028
01:38:37.427 --> 01:38:38.506
<b>Yes.</b>

1029
01:38:39.335 --> 01:38:41.113
<b>I was trembling.</b>

1030
01:38:42.342 --> 01:38:44.060
<b>You were so flimsy.</b>

1031
01:38:44.260 --> 01:38:47.127
<b>I thought, "So this is how you are."</b>

1032
01:38:50.034 --> 01:38:52.032
<b>You turned into a fine man,</b>

1033
01:38:52.082 --> 01:38:53.331
<b>Kazuto.</b>

1034
01:38:57.387 --> 01:38:58.656
<b>Not really.</b>

1035
01:38:59.805 --> 01:39:02.782
<b>It's all because of the people surrounding me.</b>

1036
01:39:04.220 --> 01:39:05.849
<b>Have you come up with</b>

1037
01:39:06.078 --> 01:39:07.677
<b>a name for the pub?</b>

1038
01:39:11.213 --> 01:39:12.612
<b>"Matsuri"…</b>

1039
01:39:13.011 --> 01:39:15.279
<b>is what I have in mind.</b>

1040
01:39:20.394 --> 01:39:21.653
<b>I see.</b>

1041
01:39:23.101 --> 01:39:25.119
<b>Once you open your store…</b>

1042
01:39:26.558 --> 01:39:28.446
<b>you should let her know.</b>

1043
01:39:42.762 --> 01:39:44.700
<b>Is the novel completed?</b>

1044
01:39:46.348 --> 01:39:50.064
<b>I wrote a lot of bad things
about you in it, though.</b>


1045
01:39:50.454 --> 01:39:53.371
<b>That you didn't bring me to the Skytree.</b>

1046
01:39:53.581 --> 01:39:55.499
<b>Oh, stop it, will you?</b>

1047
01:39:56.448 --> 01:39:57.627
<b>It's fine.</b>

1048
01:39:57.727 --> 01:39:59.605
<b>It's just fiction, after all.</b>

1049
01:40:00.644 --> 01:40:03.851
<b>I added in the book
that you're having a baby.</b>


1050
01:40:04.100 --> 01:40:04.740
<b>What?</b>

1051
01:40:07.976 --> 01:40:09.575
<b>Are you a psychic?</b>

1052
01:40:10.983 --> 01:40:12.212
<b>No way.</b>

1053
01:40:16.448 --> 01:40:18.026
<b>I'm pregnant.</b>

1054
01:40:22.762 --> 01:40:24.610
<b>I'm in my second month now,</b>

1055
01:40:25.349 --> 01:40:27.717
<b>and I'll be giving birth
next year by the summer.</b>


1056
01:40:32.712 --> 01:40:35.099
<b>Will I be able to hold him?</b>

1057
01:40:37.247 --> 01:40:39.405
<b>Of course you can!</b>

1058
01:40:41.223 --> 01:40:43.850
<b>You can even help me
come up with a name, too.</b>


1059
01:40:50.024 --> 01:40:52.512
<b>Sorry, big sis.</b>

1060
01:40:55.699 --> 01:40:58.186
<b>I said awful things to you.</b>

1061
01:40:59.735 --> 01:41:02.112
<b>I've always regretted it.</b>

1062
01:41:05.139 --> 01:41:07.916
<b>The fact that you're trying to save me…</b>

1063
01:41:09.305 --> 01:41:12.662
<b>and even praying for me
until the very last moment.</b>


1064
01:41:13.681 --> 01:41:15.239
<b>Thank you.</b>

1065
01:41:20.364 --> 01:41:25.539
<b>I'm really glad that you stayed
as the same old, big sister I've known.</b>


1066
01:41:34.150 --> 01:41:36.398
<b>What are you crying about?</b>

1067
01:41:36.777 --> 01:41:38.256
<b>Shut up!</b>

1068
01:41:46.488 --> 01:41:47.737
<b>Thanks.</b>

1069
01:41:51.273 --> 01:41:54.829
<b>- Hey, long time no see! Good work!
- It's been a while!</b>


1070
01:41:55.768 --> 01:41:57.986
<b>- Amazing! I've always wanted to come here.
- Woah, quite a lot.</b>


1071
01:41:58.036 --> 01:42:00.743
<b>- We're barging in!
- Hey, welcome!</b>


1072
01:42:00.793 --> 01:42:03.451
<b>- Woah, this is a great place!
- Excuse me.</b>


1073
01:42:03.551 --> 01:42:04.819
<b>I'm sorry, coming through.</b>

1074
01:42:04.889 --> 01:42:06.238
<b>Sorry, we're passing by
behind you.</b>


1075
01:42:06.328 --> 01:42:08.436
<b>Hey, Kazu! Congrats!</b>

1076
01:42:08.686 --> 01:42:09.744
<b>Congrats!</b>

1077
01:42:09.844 --> 01:42:11.133
<b>Really? Thank you!</b>

1078
01:42:11.223 --> 01:42:14.819
<b>- It's an occasion, so I brought with me my ex.
- Watch your words.</b>


1079
01:42:19.635 --> 01:42:20.564
<b>Here.</b>

1080
01:42:20.893 --> 01:42:24.200
<b>To celebrate your opening.
Open it after work.</b>


1081
01:42:25.429 --> 01:42:27.487
<b>It'll be on public sale next month.</b>

1082
01:42:29.655 --> 01:42:32.412
<b>- In the meanwhile, we'd like 2 beers.
- Yes! Coming right up.</b>


1083
01:42:32.542 --> 01:42:34.949
<b>- Excuse me!
- Yes, on my way!</b>


1084
01:42:36.757 --> 01:42:38.256
<b>Seriously.</b>

1085
01:42:38.436 --> 01:42:41.663
<b>A man who can really take
good care of others.</b>


1086
01:42:42.642 --> 01:42:44.390
<b>You're right.</b>

1087
01:42:46.518 --> 01:42:48.885
<b>I hope it reaches a lot of people.</b>

1088
01:42:52.652 --> 01:42:54.000
<b>It will.</b>

1089
01:42:54.500 --> 01:42:55.758
<b>For sure.</b>

1090
01:43:22.841 --> 01:43:24.999
<b><i>You're not gonna slide down?</i></b>

1091
01:43:25.099 --> 01:43:27.457
<b><i>I'd die. 
I'm sick, remember?</i></b>

1092
01:43:27.647 --> 01:43:30.294
<b><i>Then, you know…</i></b>

1093
01:43:31.253 --> 01:43:33.660
<b><i>Wanna try that out?</i></b>

1094
01:43:34.000 --> 01:43:36.957
<b><i>- It's embarrassing! I'd be too embarrassed!
